# CodeAlpha - Phishing Awareness Training

## Objective

The objective of this project is to educate users about phishing attacks, social engineering techniques, and online security practices.

## Topics Covered

* Introduction to Phishing
* Types of Phishing Attacks
* Fake Websites and Emails
* Social Engineering Techniques
* Best Security Practices
* Real-World Examples
* Interactive Quiz

## Tools Used

* Microsoft PowerPoint / Google Slides
* Kali Linux
* Web Browser

## Deliverables

* Awareness Presentation
* Quiz Questions
* Screenshots
* Video Demonstration

